name: Smoothe Kila - Shiny Ditto
description: You wanna know whats wrong with our friend here ? Well theres a list. Driven by a massive Ego and drive for compliments he commits only one crime: Assination. He has a 100% perfect kill ratio and that goes to his head much like the happy pills he takes to chill. You can catch a glimpse of him waddling down the street singing, "Give me compliments, I said give me compliments." On his off days. His mental stuability is never up for discussion and he certainly likes Russian woman over any other according to what I've read. Beware because he can morph into anything and anyone......
